product.description: This Effect makes the triggering user join a team of your choosing.

product.name: WIRED Effect: Move And Rotate Furni

product.name: WIRED Effect: Timer Reset
product.description: This Effect resets triggers that use timers.

product.name: WIRED Effect: Show Message
product.description: This effect shows a secret message only to the triggering users.
